= CloseCall

* http://.rubyforge.org
* http://.rubyforge.org/closecall


== DESCRIPTION

CloseCall is a mixin that allows programs to make slight spelling 
and/or arity mistakes on method calls and the program will still work.


== RELEASE NOTES

Please see RELEASE file.


== SYNOPSIS

  class X
    include CloseCall
    def demonstrate
      "DEMONSTATED!"
    end
  end

  X.new.demnstrate  #=> DEMONSTRATED!


== HOW TO INSTALL

To install with RubyGems simply open a console and type:

  gem install closecall

Local installation requires Setup.rb (gem install setup),
then download the tarball package and type:

  tar -xvzf closecall-1.0.0.tgz
  cd closecall-1.0.0.tgz
  sudo setup.rb all

Windows users use 'ruby setup.rb all'.


